title: Bonnie Watson Coleman
added: In the summer of 2018, Watson Coleman underwent surgery to remove a cancerous tumor.<ref>{{Cite web|last=NJ.com|first=Brent Johnson {{!}} NJ Advance Media for|date=2018-11-02|title=N.J. congresswoman recovering after cancerous tumor was removed|url=https://www.nj.com/politics/2018/11/watson_coleman_recovering_after_cancerous_growth_w.html|access-date=2021-01-11|website=nj|language=en}}</ref>

title: Bonnie Watson Coleman
added: In 1972, Watson married Jim Carter. They had one son together. The pair divorced in the early 1980's. In 1995, she married William Coleman. Her second husband has two sons from a previous marriage.<ref>{{Cite news|last=Ginsberg|first=Wendy|date=2002-05-05|title=IN PERSON; The Family Business (Published 2002)|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/05/05/nyregion/in-person-the-family-business.html|access-date=2021-01-11|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>
